<h1> There's your actual recipe</h1>
<p>Name: <%=@recette.name%></p>
<p>Ingredients:</p>
<ul>
  <%@recette.ingredients.split(" ").each do |r|%>
    <li><%= r %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
<p>Ingredients: <%=@recette.ingredients%></p>
<p>Cook Time: <%=@recette.cook_time%> minutes</p>

<p>Do you want to modify your <a href="/recipes/<%=@recette.id%>/edit">recipy</a>?</p>
<p>Or Do you want to <a href="/recipes/<%=@recette.id%>/delete">delete your recipe</a>?</p>

<h1>Please Delete your recipe</h1>
<form action='/recipes/<%=@recette.id%>/delete' method="post">
<input id="hidden" type="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
    <label for="name">Name:</label>
    <input type="text" name="name" value="<%=@recette.name%>">
    <label for="ingredients">Ingredients:</label>
    <textarea name="ingredients" rows="10" cols="80"><%=@recette.ingredients%></textarea>
    <label for="cook_time">Cook Time:</label>
    <input type="text" name="cook_time" value="<%=@recette.cook_time%>">
    <input type="submit" value="Delete">
</form>
